{"tid":2203232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共黨媒被踢爆用遙控機「耀武揚威」 網友揶揄：自欺欺人","createTime":"2020-09-15T07:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T08:50:16.000Z","uid":337052,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7546eff87a3b64b15e85ef7a2b24d922a7febb5c","tid":2203232,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:55:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中共黨媒被踢爆用遙控機「耀武揚威」 網友揶揄：自欺欺人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/p7PqNN6O_wt2sOuZ7UeC4WM1r3E=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HL5CIWUAR5HFXFIS43DBPGGSIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp7PqNN6O_wt2sOuZ7UeC4WM1r3E%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHL5CIWUAR5HFXFIS43DBPGGSIA.jpg&h=ba1235af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《人民日報》在推特發文指，影片中戰機做90度爬升的高難度動作，卻被網友踢爆該架根本只是遙控飛機。翻攝推特<br />\n台海局勢近日轉趨緊張，中國頻頻對台灣進行各種軍演挑釁，想不到就連遙控飛機做出低空90度爬升的高難度動作，也被中共喉舌《人民日報》當成軍機般來「耀武揚威」，卻遭不少外國網友嘲笑：「用遙控飛機打得贏台灣或印度嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》日前在推特（twitter）上發布一段影片，片中可見一架疑似殲-11或蘇-27的「戰機」，從空中俯衝至跑道後，貼著地面低空飛行，隨後突然90度爬升飛向天際，還做出翻轉等特技動作。<span class=\"red\">《人民日報》指，這是中國航空研究院（Chinese Aeronautical Establishment）釋出的培訓影片，「戰機」做出如此高難度動作令人印象深刻。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，有網友發現，在影片中有一名站在跑道旁的男子，身邊就停著一架遙控飛機，而該名男子手上疑似拿著遙控器，操控飛行中的「戰機」，且該架戰機發出的聲音也與正規戰機的引擎聲並不相同，與跑道的比例更可顯見，它並非解放軍正規戰機。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">許多網友對於中國官媒釋出的影片感到不以為然，還留言揶揄「你們要用這個和台灣或印度作戰嗎？」「就決定用這個和台灣的F-16V或印度的飆風戰機對決了！」、「自欺欺人中國最強」。</span>（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200915/IDYLODVNLBBYFEBJZTHZAEUZOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200915%2FIDYLODVNLBBYFEBJZTHZAEUZOY%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=8ce61b47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200915%2FIDYLODVNLBBYFEBJZTHZAEUZOY%2F&h=248fe8c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200915/IDYLODVNLBBYFEBJZTHZAEUZOY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/PDChina/status/1303349876378406913?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPDChina%2Fstatus%2F1303349876378406913%3Fs%3D20&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=28e8bb3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPDChina%2Fstatus%2F1303349876378406913%3Fs%3D20&h=709fb70b\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/PDChina/status/1303349876378406913?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"7b2bad93af8e1bd41e01bf3abc913dd39e0b2c8f","tid":2203232,"uid":369075,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:56:19.000Z","msg":"其實整咁大架遙控機除左扮野仲有咩實際用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c2539da03211f102faba6049a1e38ce5d0adbf","tid":2203232,"uid":218081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:58:04.000Z","msg":"屌，連打飛機都要拎技膠陽具玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6683efb60d63f9174f5c32f0cb58a6825e0f6b9","tid":2203232,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:00:38.000Z","msg":"「你們要用這個和台灣或印度作戰嗎？」「就決定用這個和台灣的F-16V或印度的飆風戰機對決了！」"},{"pid":"9fa3d727828b28a78db5bf537d0375bc87680027","tid":2203232,"uid":218699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b2bad93af8e1bd41e01bf3abc913dd39e0b2c8f","tid":2203232,"uid":369075,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:56:19.000Z","msg":"其實整咁大架遙控機除左扮野仲有咩實際用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:01:57.000Z","msg":"當無人機用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f